      "Increased uric acid: Can elevate uric acid levels in the blood, potentially leading to gout attacks.",
      "Photosensitivity: May increase sensitivity to sunlight, resulting in a higher risk of sunburn.",
      "Gastrointestinal issues: Possible side effects include nausea, vomiting, or diarrhea.",
      "Fatigue: Patients may experience feelings of tiredness or weakness."
